ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: A superficial review of the essential comedies of the spanish golden age

Very useful for knowledge of drama, and specifically Comedia, of the period, the instructor very helpful, knowledgeable and kind, but class time could've been better spent.On the whole I would recommend the course, but with the above caveat.
I would recommend it because the texts covered are interesting and are essential for the comp exams.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: This course is not directly in my area of interest, but it was invaluable for my studying of the comprehensive exam material and it provides a foundation for the more modern literature which is my main focus.
